---
alwaysApply: true
---

### ContentCard — standard portrait card:
- Aspect ratio: 2:3
- Border radius: 16px outer container, 12px internal elements
- No borders — background colour defines card edge
- Rating badge: top-right overlay, `surface_container_highest` background, `primary_container` star icon
- Title: `title-lg` typography token, `on_surface`
- Subtitle (year • genre): `label-sm`, `on_surface_variant`
- `posterPath` may be null — always handle: show `surface_container_high` placeholder with centred StreamList icon, never a broken image

### SkeletonCard — required for every async section:
- Shape must match the content it replaces (portrait rectangle for cards, circle for cast avatars, wide rectangle for text)
- Base colour: `surface_container_high`
- Shimmer: animated opacity or gradient sweep between `surface_container_high` and `surface_bright`
- Animation duration: ~1500ms loop
- Never use ActivityIndicator/spinner as a substitute for skeleton loading

### Buttons:
- Primary CTA: `react-native-linear-gradient` with `['#FFB3AE', '#FF5351']`, start `{x:0,y:0}`, end `{x:1,y:1}`
- Secondary: `surface_container_highest` background, `on_surface` text
- "In Watchlist" state: `surface_container_highest` background, `outline_variant` border at 15% opacity, `primary_container` icon
